<!DOCTYPE html>
<!--[if IE 9 ]><html class="ie ie9 no-js" lang="en"><![endif]-->
<!--[if gt IE 9 | !IE]><!-->
<html class="no-js" lang="en">
<!--<![endif]-->
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <title>TDPJ</title>
  <meta name="description" content="A bunch of free EdTech tools made by real life teachers.">
  <meta name="keywords" content="EdTech, Free, Discussion Boards, Timeline">
  <meta name="author" content="Jeff Maxim">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1">
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="assets/img/apple-touch-icon.png">
  <link rel="icon" href="assets/img/favicon.ico">

  <%= stylesheet_link_tag "landing/bootstrap.min" %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag "landing/vendor" %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag "landing/style" %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag "landing/hoc_custom" %>
  <!--[if lte IE 9]><!-->
  <%= javascript_include_tag "landing/vendor/html5shiv.min.js" %>
  <!--<![endif]-->
</head>
<body>

  <div class="site">
    <div class="site-loader">
      <div class="site-loader-spinner"></div>
    </div> <!-- .site-loader -->

    <div class="site-canvas">
      <header class="site-header">
        <nav class="navbar navbar-theme">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="navbar-header">

              <div class="navbar-brand-wrap">
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">
                  <%= image_tag("site-header-logo-2.png") %>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div> <!-- .navbar-header -->


          </div>
        </nav>
      </header> <!-- .site-header -->
      <main class="site-main">
        <div id="intro" class="section block-default align-c-xs-max">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="row row-table">
              <div class="col-sm-12">
                <div class="col-inner">
                  <div class="section-heading">
                    <h2>Hour of Code!</h2>
                    <p>
                      Today you'll learn about <b>Hour of Code</b> and how to implement it in your classroom. This website will live here forever, so you can some back and use
                      these resources whenever you want :)
                    </p>
                    <p>
                      If there's some typos, I apologize, but you can correct
                      them <a href='https://github.com/jeffthemaximum/Teachers-Dont-Pay-Jeff'>here</a> if you want.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                      You can learn more about me <a href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/jeffmaxim/'>here!</a>
                    </p>
                    <h4>
                      tl;dr
                    </h4>
                    <ul>
                      <li>
                        What is Hour of Code?
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        What can I do for Hour of Code?
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        What are the associated standards?
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        Why teach coding?
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        How does coding progress from K-5 and beyond?
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        You don't have to know how to code to teach how to code!
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        What are the associated standards?
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        Coding vs. Computer Science
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        Doing and Discovery works best
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        How to keep momentum after Hour of Code?
                      </li>

                    </ul>
                  </div> <!-- .section-heading -->
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-sm-6 m-t-60-xs-max p-l-60-md-min">
                <div class="col-inner clearfix">
                  <%= image_tag("landing-1.jpg", class: "img-responsive float-r-sm-min m-x-auto-xs-max", data: {sr: "right"}) %>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div> <!-- #brief_1 -->

        <div id="brief_2" class="section block-warning align-c-xs-max">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="row row-table">
              <div class="col-sm-6 m-b-60-xs-max p-r-60-md-min">
                <div class="col-inner clearfix">
                  <%= image_tag("landing-2.jpg", class: "img-responsive float-l-sm-min m-x-auto-xs-max", data: {sr: "left"}) %>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-sm-6">
                <div class="col-inner">
                  <div class="section-heading">
                    <h2>What is Hour of Code?</h2>
                  </div> <!-- .section-heading -->
                  <div class="section-content">
                    <ul>
                      <li>
                        The main hour of code website is <a href='https://hourofcode.com/us'>here</a>
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        The intro video is <a href='https://youtu.be/SrnvvWDm73k'>here</a>
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        The activities are <a href='https://hourofcode.com/us/learn'>here</a>. You can filter by
                        age, grade, experience level, and many other things.
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        The activities are <a href='https://hourofcode.com/us/learn'>here</a>. You can filter by
                        age, grade, experience level, and many other things. My favorite are the Social Studies
                        and Language Arts activities!
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        Use those activities above and try it out! You have 10 minutes. This is you DO NOW!
                        Can't one to choose? Try this one <a href='https://game.kodable.com/hour-of-code'>here</a>.
                      </li>
                    </ul>
                  </div> <!-- .section-content -->
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div> <!-- #brief_2 -->

        <div id="brief_3" class="section block-success align-c-xs-max">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="row row-table">
              <div class="col-sm-6">
                <div class="col-inner">
                  <div class="section-heading">
                    <h5>Open to feedback</h5>
                    <h2>Always adding more tools!</h2>
                    <p>We want to make stuff that you want to use! Have an idea for a free EdTech tool that you want? Let us know!</p>
                  </div> <!-- .section-heading -->
                  <div class="section-content">


                    <a class="btn btn-invert m-y-5" href="#contact">Contact us</a>
                  </div> <!-- .section-content -->
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-sm-6 m-t-60-xs-max p-l-60-md-min">
                <div class="col-inner clearfix">
                  <%= image_tag("landing-3.jpg", class: "img-responsive float-r-sm-min m-x-auto-xs-max", data: {sr: "right"}) %>

                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div> <!-- #brief_3 -->

        <div id="contact" class="section block-default">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="section-heading text-center">

              <h2>Get in touch with us</h2>
              <p> Do you love <b>Teachers don't pay Jeff</b>? Hate it? Have a question? Let us know :)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="row section-content m-t-60-sm-min">
              <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-5">
                <div class="col-inner">

                  <div class="icon-box _left">
                    <div class="icon-box-media">
                      <%= image_tag("icon/mail.png", data: {sr: "bottom"}) %>
                    </div>
                    <div class="icon-box-heading">
                      <h4>Email Address</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="icon-box-content font-sub font-italic">
                      <span>frey.maxim@gmail.com</span>
                      <br>
                      <span>jeff@mrmaxim.org</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <div class="icon-box _left">
                    <div class="icon-box-media">
                      <%= image_tag("icon/pin.png", data: {sr: "bottom"}) %>
                    </div>
                    <div class="icon-box-heading">
                      <h4>Address</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="icon-box-content font-sub font-italic">
                      <span>305 West 92nd Street</span>
                      <br>
                      <span>New York, NY 10025</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-offset-1 m-t-60-xs-max">
                <div class="col-inner">
                  <%= form_for @contact_request, :html => {:class => '_default', :id => 'contactForm'} do |f| %>
                    <div class="form-group required">
                      <label class="form-label" for="contactName">Your name</label>
                      <%= f.text_field :name, class: "form-control", id: "contactName" %>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group required">
                      <label class="form-label" for="contactEmail">Email address</label>
                      <%= f.text_field :email, class: "form-control", id: "contactName" %>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group required">
                      <label class="form-label" for="contactMessage">Message</label>
                      <%= f.text_area :message, class: "form-control", id: "contactName", rows: 4 %>
                    </div>
                    <div class="btn-wrap">
                      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Send Message</button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-notify"></div>
                  </form> <!-- #contactForm -->
                <% end %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div> <!-- #contact -->
        <div id="map-canvas"></div> <!-- #map-canvas -->
      </main> <!-- .site-main -->
      <footer class="site-footer block-invert">
        <div class="container">
          <%= image_tag("site-header-logo-2.png", class: "site-footer-logo img-responsive", data: {sr: "bottom"}) %>
          <ul class="site-footer-social-list">
            <li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/frey.maxim" target="_blank">Facebook</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://twitter.com/jeffthemaximum" target="_blank">Twitter</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.instagram.com/jeffthemaximum/" target="_blank">Instagram</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jeffmaxim/" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a></li>
          </ul>
          <p class="site-footer-copyright">2017 © <a href="#" target="_blank">Jeff Maxim</a> | all rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
      </footer> <!-- .site-footer -->
    </div>
  </div>

  <%= javascript_include_tag "landing/vendor/jquery-1.11.3.min.js" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "landing/vendor/bootstrap.min.js" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "landing/vendor/plugin.js" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "landing/variable.js" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "landing/main.js" %>

